---
layout: default.hbs
subject: \{{#if isStudent}}You’ve been added as a student member of \{{ org.name }} on NKBA.org\{{else}}You've been added as to \{{ org.name }} on the new NKBA.org\{{/if}}
---

<span class="preheader">
    \{{#if isStudent}}
        You’ve been added as a student member of \{{ org.name }} on NKBA.org
    \{{else}}
        You've been added as an employee of \{{ org.name }} on the new NKBA.org
    \{{/if}}
</span>
<table class="header" align="center"  width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#FDFDFE"  border="0">
    <tr>
        <td class="wrapper border-bottom" valign="middle">
            <a href="\{{WEB_URL}}"><img class="logo" border="0" src="https://media.nkba.org/img/nkba-logo@2x.png" alt="NKBA" height="30" width="141"></a>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<table class="main" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
    <tr>
        <td class="wrapper">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4 pt1 " valign="top">
                        <h2 class="bold">
                            \{{#if isStudent}}
                                You've been added as a student member of \{{ org.name }} on NKBA.org.
                                \{{else}}
                                You've been added to the \{{ org.name }} organization on NKBA.org. 
                            \{{/if}}
                        </h2>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4" valign="top">
                       Your complimentary NKBA membership is sponsored by Monogram.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4" valign="top">
                       If you believe this move was made in error, please call the NKBA Member Services team at 1-800-THE-NKBA or send an email to <a href="mailto:info@nkba.org">info@nkba.org</a>. 
                    </td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4" valign="top">
                      Thank you,<br>
                      The NKBA
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
